Package: anatembea
Title: AnteNatal Assessment of Temporal Malaria Epidemiology using Mechanistic Models, Bayesian Estimation, and Analysis
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Joseph", "Hicks", email = "joe.tal.hicks@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: A tool for AnteNatal Assessment of Temporal Malaria Epidemiology using Mechanistic Models, Bayesian Estimation, and Analysis. This open-source R package attempts to address this problem by translating monthly ANC1 prevalence into seasonal patterns in malaria transmission and clinical cases.
